  "detailed_description": "Introducing Cat Sandbox - guide cute cats through puzzles! Safely lead them to comfy cardboard homes using physics and destruction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cat-saving Adventure</h2>Help cute cats find their way home! Use tools like bombs, mines, sand, and water to create paths. Watch the magic happen as everything reacts!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/0cca36b6d9a7a87d03b406f7ce3c0fe1.poster.avif?t=1770814446\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/0cca36b6d9a7a87d03b406f7ce3c0fe1.webm?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/0cca36b6d9a7a87d03b406f7ce3c0fe1.mp4?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nostalgic Pixel Art</h2>Enjoy classic pixel art style cats. It's like a cozy blanket for cat lovers and gamers!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/d388a2c1115b2cd596ba7616fac3afdf.poster.avif?t=1770814446\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/d388a2c1115b2cd596ba7616fac3afdf.webm?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/d388a2c1115b2cd596ba7616fac3afdf.mp4?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fun Physics Puzzles</h2>Every level is a new puzzle adventure! Think and plan your moves. Each one counts. See your solution come to life!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/734b4c3898d5158d6b227b1353a5d0a9.poster.avif?t=1770814446\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/734b4c3898d5158d6b227b1353a5d0a9.webm?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/734b4c3898d5158d6b227b1353a5d0a9.mp4?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For Cat Lovers</h2>If you love cats, this game is for you. Guide them step by step to safety. Cat Sandbox is our way of saying \"we love cats!\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/8ac8b0589714113fa762da2337baa2cc.poster.avif?t=1770814446\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/8ac8b0589714113fa762da2337baa2cc.webm?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/8ac8b0589714113fa762da2337baa2cc.mp4?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the Fun</h2>Download Cat Sandbox now and start your cat-saving adventure!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/33d7362d0a4c20d21d7ad656f7735c0c.poster.avif?t=1770814446\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/33d7362d0a4c20d21d7ad656f7735c0c.webm?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698300/extras/33d7362d0a4c20d21d7ad656f7735c0c.mp4?t=1770814446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
